title: Tiangong-1, Long March-2FT1 separate
description: JIUQUAN, Sept. 29 (Xinhua) -- The Tiangong-1 space lab module successfully separated from the second stage of Long March-2FT1 carrier rocket at a height of about 200 kilometers above the Earth.
